data.description: Welcome to 947 Byrnderwen Pl located in Hampton Hills Subdivision in Lyman, South Carolina. This two-story home boasts of a spacious family room with a cozy fireplace that opens up to a well-appointed kitchen. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a gas range, microwave, and dishwasher, and features an expansive granite island, recessed lighting, and a tile backsplash. The master suite is located on the second floor featuring  an oversized shower, a separate garden tub, dual vanities, and a large walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms  and loft area are also located on the second floor along with a full bathroom. Additional features of this home include 9-foot first-floor ceilings, hardwood laminate flooring on the main level, a 2-car garage with garage door openers, an oak handrail with metal spindles at the first floor, and a tankless hot water heater. Plus, the home is located on a corner lot with one of the biggest yards in the subdivision.
